# Python Command Execution

- In this Python project, always run Python tooling with `.venv/bin/python`.
- Do not use system Python interpreters such as `/opt/homebrew/bin/python`, `/opt/homebrew/bin/python3.12`, `/usr/bin/python`, or `python3`.
- Examples:
  - Use `.venv/bin/python -m pytest`.
  - Use `.venv/bin/python -m py_compile path/to/file.py`.
  - Use `.venv/bin/python -m pip` only if dependency installation is explicitly needed.
